since%20the%20last%20triage%20run.%20Read%20the%20full%20body%20of%20any%20confirmation%20or%20cancellation%20%E2%80%94%20snippets%20are%20not%20enough.%20Note%20the%20date%20range%20scanned%20in%20the%20triage%20summary.%0A%0A%23%23%20STEP%201.5%20%E2%80%94%20SWAP%20RECIPROCITY%20AUDIT%20%28CRITICAL%20%E2%80%94%20runs%20every%20triage%29%0AThis%20step%20exists%20because%20of%20a%20confirmed%2C%20repeated%20failure%20pattern%3A%20when%20a%20swap%20is%20accepted%2C%20only%20the%20inbound%20%28%F0%9F%93%A3%29%20row%20tends%20to%20get%20created%20in%20the%20tracker.%20The%20outbound%20%28%E2%99%A5%EF%B8%8F%29%20obligation%20row%20is%20frequently%20missed%2C%20leading%20to%20missed%20sends.%0A%0AAdditionally%2C%20some%20swaps%20are%20accepted%20directly%20on%20the%20BookClicker%20website%20with%20no%20acceptance%20email%20ever%20hitting%20Gmail.%0A%0AThe%20Rule%3A%20SWAPPED%20%3D%20TWO%20ROWS%2C%20ALWAYS%0AEvery%20swap%20has%20two%20legs%3A%0A-%20%F0%9F%93%A3%20Inbound%20%E2%80%94%20they%20promote%20your%20book%20on%20Date%20A%0A-%20%E2%99%A5%EF%B8%8F%20Outbound%20%E2%80%94%20you%20promote%20their%20book%20on%20Date%20B%0ADate%20A%20and%20Date%20B%20are%20often%20different%20dates.%0A%0AHow%20to%20Run%20This%20Audit%3A%0AA%29%20After%20processing%20all%20emails%20in%20Step%201%2C%20check%20your%20tracker%20for%20ALL%20%F0%9F%93%A3%20rows%20where%20Payment%20Type%20%3D%20Swap%20and%20Promo%20Date%20is%20within%20the%20next%2030%20days.%20For%20each%20%F0%9F%93%A3%20swap%20row%20found%3A%0A-%20Search%20the%20tracker%20for%20a%20matching%20%E2%99%A5%EF%B8%8F%20row%20with%20the%20same%20partner%20name%0A-%20If%20NO%20matching%20%E2%99%A5%EF%B8%8F%20row%20exists%20%E2%86%92%20%F0%9F%9A%A8%20FLAG%20IMMEDIATELY%0A-%20Search%20Gmail%20for%20the%20acceptance%20email%20to%20find%20the%20outbound%20date%20and%20book%20details%0A-%20If%20no%20acceptance%20email%20found%20%E2%86%92%20flag%20to%20author%0A-%20Create%20the%20missing%20%E2%99%A5%EF%B8%8F%20row%20with%20all%20available%